Package misc

Class CRDBInterfaceInitialiser

  • Object
    • CRDBInterfaceInitialiser
  • public class CRDBInterfaceInitialiser
extends Object
    Represents a class whose sole purpose is to call the static function to initialise both Camp Databases and Registration databases to ensure both databases have the interfaces they require from each other.

    2023-11-17

      • InitialiseCRDataBaseInterfaces

        public static void InitialiseCRDataBaseInterfaces​(CampDataBase campDataBase,
                                                  RegistrationDataBase registrationDataBase)
        Further initialises the various interfaces within both the camp database and the registration database. This method should be called instantly after camp database and registration database objects have already been instantiated.
        Parameters:
        campDataBase - The camp database object to be further initialised with registration database interfaces.
        registrationDataBase - THe registration database object to be further intiialised with camp database interfaces.
